Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很清静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 公瑾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然站了起来 就不要提了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才发现 这里真的很清静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 小蒙也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会淹死的 公瑾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经告诉你你想知道的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能告诉你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路的话还是要你自己选择
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后不会再见面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子
